FuncDef: This command configures start and end labels for a reserved label block. This command must be configured for a reserved label block to be created.

ParaDef.Info: Specifies a starting value. Values-18432 to 524287 within dynamic label range | 1048575 (FP4 only).
Specifies an ending value. Values-18432 to 524287 within dynamic label range | 1048575 (FP4 only).
